{"tid":485758,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"DC日本動畫作品 - 《忍者蝙蝠俠》首部預告公佈！","createTime":"2017-12-01T08:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T13:22:09.000Z","uid":64191,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ee93b7a16668ba22152770d621a2fed555cb42a3","tid":485758,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wId8XY6y_HA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwId8XY6y_HA&d=R5uB2q%2F6rUkR92WZqqw0yTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=075f3de2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wId8XY6y_HA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QF031DwMffQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQF031DwMffQ&d=R5uB2q%2F6rUkR92WZqqw0yTM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=82fec64b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QF031DwMffQ</a><br />\n<br />\n由神風動畫耗時 3 年，製作的長篇動畫系列，將美國 DC 漫畫旗下有錢又知名的超級英雄「蝙蝠俠」穿越到戰國時代，並且將反派「小丑」塑造成第六天魔王的形象，讓觀眾在熟悉的西方超級英雄角色，結合熟悉的東方背景，誕生不同風貌的動畫長篇故事。<br />\n<br />\n預定2018年在日本上映<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【製作陣容】<br />\n<br />\n導演：水﨑淳平（「JOJO的奇幻冒險」系列片頭）<br />\n劇本：中島かずき（「天元突破 紅蓮螺巖」、「Kill la Kill」）<br />\n配樂：菅野祐悟（「PSYCHO-PASS」）<br />\n製作公司：神風動画（「JOJO的奇幻冒險」系列片頭、「勇者鬥惡龍」系列片頭）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【配音陣容】<br />\n<br />\n蝙蝠俠：山寺宏一<br />\n小丑：高木渉<br />\n貓女：加隈亜衣<br />\n哈莉&middot;奎茵：釘宮理恵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時已知見到歷代羅賓、Deathstroke、Gorilla Grodd。難怪近年見唔到神風動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19d133682cf15f3fcbdf0992019da9aab795bc9","tid":485758,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:34:04.000Z","msg":"畫風好正"},{"pid":"75137cc493e5926575828b0e4a72d5f45ce73f7c","tid":485758,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"好撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3fbf055044e41c8bae1dec0453bb2e91660b4e","tid":485758,"uid":81397